javelin.model.feat

Class BullRush

  • java.lang.Object
    • javelin.model.feat.Feat
      • javelin.model.feat.BullRush
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class BullRush
extends Feat
    This works a bit differently than in the official rules: on a successful charge it automatically pushes the opponent back 5 feet, causing no attacks of opportunity. Not otherwise available to prevent overloading the AI with options.
